      /***************************************************************
      *NOTES:    None.                                               *
      *                                                              *
      *FLOW:     This program will display the Driver menu, PWK06.   *
      *          PWK06 displays a list of drivers that are on the    *
      *          data collect file(FDK02) for this policy.  From     *
      *          this screen the following options are available:    *
      *          CF1, CF2 & CF24 - Will exit this program.           *
      *          CF3 - Will display the subfile starting with        *
      *                driver number 1.                              *
      *          CF5 - Will display the next 13 driver names.        *
      *          CF7 - When a driver number is entered, this         *
      *                displays the driver detail information        *
      *                screen (PWK07) with fields initialized        *
      *                to spaces so that a new driver maybe added.   *
      *                This screen has the same options for ENTER-   *
      *                KEY below.                                    *
      *          CF10 - And the cursor is positioned next to a driver,
      *                This will cause that driver to be deleted off *
      *                the data collect file(FDK02).                 *
      *          ENTER-KEY - And the cursor is positioned next to a  *
      *                driver, this will cause the driver detail     *
      *                information screen to be displayed. Edits     *
      *                are performed on this screen and all infor-   *
      *                mation must be correct before processing      *
      *                continues.  From this screen the following    *
      *                functions maybe performed:                    *
      *                CF1 & CF2 - Exit logic after updateing the    *
      *                      data collect file(FDK02). CF1 will      *
      *                      exit the program.                       *
      *                CF24 - Exit logic without updateing any       *
      *                      files.                                  *
      *                CF3 - Will display screen PWK08, this is      *
      *                      the violation & accident detail in-     *
      *                      formation map.  Data entered on this    *
      *                      screen is edited and must be correct    *
      *                      before the data collect file(FDK03)     *
      *                      is updated.  From this screen the       *
      *                      user has options:                       *
      *                      CF1, CF2 & CF3 - To update the data col-*
      *                             lect file(FDK03) and exit logic. *
      *                             CF1 will exit the program.       *
      *                      CF24 - Will exit logic with out any     *
      *                             files being updated.             *
      *                      CF21 - Will exit logic and display      *
      *                             the MVR Driving Report.          *
      *
      *INSTALLATION HISTORY:
      *  Proj.
      *  No.   Name              Date       Description
      *  512   J. ARNST        03-16-92    EDIT GOOD STUDENT
      *                                    INDICATOR & DATE.
511   *  511   R. Janssen       3/28/92    Edit the Cause of Loss fields
511   *                                  found on the Violations screen.
      * 11225  J.Braun          6/26/92    Add logic to call MVR Online
      *                                    Program to Display Screen.
511   *
      * EY001  T. Prasnick      2/10/93    Mod to protect sys updated
      *                                    claims from being changed
      *                                    by user.
14358 * 14358  T. MCLAUGHLIN   11/25/02    ADDED CODE TO SUPPORT THE
14358 *                                    FINANCIAL RESPONSIBILITY
14358 *                                    INDICATORS ON DRIVER SCREEN
      /***************************************************************
      *                       PROCEDURE DIVISION                     *
      ****************************************************************

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING
                                LINKAGE-ARGUMENTS.

       000-START-PROGRAM.

13587      ACCEPT WS-CENT-DATE FROM DATE.                               TJB
13587      IF WS-CENT-YY LESS THAN CENTURY-YEAR                         TJB
13587          ADD CENTURY-100 TO WS-CENT-YY.                           TJB
13587      MOVE WS-CENT-DATE TO SYSTEM-DATE.                            TJB
           PERFORM 020-INITIALIZATION THRU 020-EXIT.

           PERFORM 100-MAIN-PROCESS THRU 100-EXIT
               UNTIL CFKEY-1  OR  CFKEY-2  OR  CFKEY-24.

           PERFORM 300-TERMINATION THRU 300-EXIT.

       010-EXIT-PROGRAM.
           EXIT PROGRAM.
      /***************************************************************
      *                       INITIALIZATION                         *
      ****************************************************************

       020-INITIALIZATION.

12038      OPEN I-O SCN                                                 TJB
12097               FDK01                                               TJB
12097               FDK04.                                              TJB
           OPEN INPUT FDK02
12097                 FDK03                                             TJB
65423                 ZDK01.


           PERFORM 025-INIT-FDK02-REC THRU 025-EXIT.
           PERFORM 030-INIT-FDK04-REC THRU 030-EXIT.

64323      EVALUATE TRUE
64323        WHEN LS-A02-STATE = "KY"
64323         AND LS-GROUP-LINE = "01"
64323          MOVE "Y" TO WS-X71-PIP-REJ-NOSPACE
64323        WHEN OTHER
64323          MOVE "N" TO WS-X71-PIP-REJ-NOSPACE
64323      END-EVALUATE.
64323
           MOVE SPACES                 TO EEV-RECORD
                                          EEM-RECORD
                                          PWKDADDS-I
                                          PWKDADDS-O
                                          WS-FEEDBACK.
           MOVE ZERO                   TO SUBFILE-KEY
                                          ROW OF PWKDADDS-I
                                          ROW OF PWKDADDS-O
                                          COP OF PWKDADDS-I
                                          COP OF PWKDADDS-O
                                           LS-CFKEY.
           PERFORM 050-LOAD-DRIVERS THRU 050-EXIT.
           MOVE "F"                    TO FIRST-TIME-SW.
           PERFORM 400-RESET-FACS THRU 400-EXIT.
           MOVE ZEROS               TO B26-M2-NAME-SEQ OF PWK06DDS-I
                                       B26-M2-NAME-SEQ OF PWK06DDS-O.
           MOVE ZEROS               TO PDA-B26-DRIVER  OF PWKDADDS-O.

           IF LS-ACTIVITY-CODE EQUAL "04"
               MOVE "NEW BUSINESS"     TO P06-TRANS
           ELSE
               IF LS-ACTIVITY-CODE EQUAL "02"
                   MOVE "  CHANGES   " TO P06-TRANS
               ELSE
                   MOVE "CORRECTION"   TO P06-TRANS.

      *    MOVE IND-OFF                TO IN32 OF PWK06DDS-O.
           MOVE IND-ON                 TO IN34 OF PWK06DDS-O.
           IF LS-DETAIL-INQUIRY
               MOVE IND-OFF            TO IN34 OF PWK06DDS-O.
13929      IF LS-GROUP-LINE EQUAL "23"                                  TJB
14414                          OR "81" OR "13" OR "71"                  TJB
13929          MOVE IND-OFF TO IN40 OF PWK07DDS-O                       TJB
13929      ELSE                                                         TJB
13929          MOVE IND-ON TO IN40 OF PWK07DDS-O.                       TJB

           MOVE SPACES                 TO ELEMENT-NO
                                          EDIT-NO.
           MOVE IF-RDRANDOM            TO RF-TYPE-IO.
           MOVE REFID-ELEMENT-EDIT-VALUE   TO R01-EEV-TABLEID.
           MOVE REFID-ELEMENT-EDIT-MESSAGE TO R01-EEM-TABLEID.
           MOVE "00"                   TO R42-EEM-LINE-NUMBER.

       020-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      /
       025-INIT-FDK02-REC.

           MOVE SPACES                 TO DATA-COLLECT-RECORD-FDK02
           COPY PCB49.

       025-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      /
       030-INIT-FDK04-REC.

           MOVE SPACES                 TO DATA-COLLECT-RECORD-FDK04
           COPY PCB37.

       030-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      /***************************************************************
      *      LOAD DRIVERS AND ASSOCIATED VEHICLES ALREADY ON POLICY  *
      ****************************************************************

       050-LOAD-DRIVERS.

           MOVE ZERO                   TO FDK02-STATUS.
           MOVE LS-POLICY-NUMBER       TO A00-M2-POL-NUM.
           MOVE LS-HISTORY-DATE        TO A30-M2-HIST-EXP-DATE.
           MOVE "DR"                   TO B25-M2-NAME-TYPE.
           START FDK02 KEY IS NOT < A00-M2-POL-NUM
                                    A30-M2-HIST-EXP-DATE
                                    B25-M2-NAME-TYPE
               INVALID KEY
                   MOVE "2"            TO FDK02-STATUS
                   PERFORM 080-CLEAR-PWK06 THRU 080-EXIT
                   MOVE IND-OFF        TO IN32 OF PWK06DDS-O
                   GO TO 050-EXIT.

       050-LOOP.

           READ FDK02 NEXT
              AT END
                 PERFORM 080-CLEAR-PWK06 THRU 080-EXIT
                 GO TO 050-EXIT.

           IF A00-M2-POL-NUM NOT EQUAL LS-POLICY-NUMBER
DLW         OR A30-M2-HIST-EXP-DATE NOT EQUAL LS-HISTORY-DATE
               PERFORM 080-CLEAR-PWK06 THRU 080-EXIT
               GO TO 050-EXIT.

           IF B25-M2-NAME-TYPE NOT EQUAL "DR"
               PERFORM 080-CLEAR-PWK06 THRU 080-EXIT
               GO TO 050-EXIT.

           IF NAME-UPDATE-SWITCH EQUAL "D"
               GO TO 050-LOOP.
           IF SUBFILE-KEY EQUAL 13
               MOVE IND-ON             TO IN31 OF PWK06DDS-O
               GO TO 050-EXIT.

           MOVE B26-M2-NAME-SEQ OF DCPOLNA TO P06-DR-NUM OF PWK06SUB-O.
           MOVE B27-MNAME OF DCPOLNA      TO P06-DR-NAME OF PWK06SUB-O.
13920      MOVE B42-MAGE OF DCPOLNA TO P06-DR-B42 OF PWK06SUB-O.        TJB
13947      MOVE B44-MMARITAL OF DCPOLNA TO P06-DR-B44 OF PWK06SUB-O.    TJB
13920      MOVE B46-MPRIN-OPER OF DCPOLNA TO P06-DR-B46 OF PWK06SUB-O.  TJB
14016      MOVE B56-MMVR-IND OF DCPOLNA TO P06-DR-MVR OF PWK06SUB-O.    TJB
14016      IF B57-MMVR-DATE OF DCPOLNA GREATER THAN ZERO                TJB
14016          MOVE B57-MMVR-DATE OF DCPOLNA TO WS-CENT-DATE            TJB
14016          MOVE WS-CENT-DATE(2:2) TO P06-DR-MVR OF PWK06SUB-O(2:2). TJB
           MOVE B47-MVEH-NUM OF DCPOLNA   TO P06-VEH     OF PWK06SUB-O.

           IF B47-MVEH-NUM OF DCPOLNA EQUAL ZERO
               MOVE "NO VEHICLE ASSIGNED"
                                       TO P06-DESCRIPTION OF PWK06SUB-O
           ELSE
               PERFORM 060-GET-VEH THRU 060-EXIT.

           ADD 1 TO SUBFILE-KEY.
12097      MOVE IND-OFF TO IN30 OF PWK06SUB-O                           TJB
12097                      IN29 OF PWK06SUB-O.                          TJB
           MOVE IND-ON                 TO IN32 OF PWK06DDS-O.
           WRITE SUBFILE CRTREC FROM PWK06SUB-O FORMAT "PWK06SUB".
           IF SUBFILE-KEY IS LESS THAN 14
               GO TO 050-LOOP.

       050-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      /
       060-GET-VEH.

           MOVE LS-POLICY-NUMBER       TO A00-M4-POL-NUM.
           MOVE LS-HISTORY-DATE        TO A30-M4-HIST-EXP-DATE.
           START FDK04 KEY IS NOT LESS THAN A00-M4-POL-NUM
                                            A30-M4-HIST-EXP-DATE
           INVALID KEY
              MOVE "NO MATCH FOR VEHICLE AND DRIVER"
                        TO P06-DESCRIPTION OF PWK06SUB-O
              GO TO 060-EXIT.

       060-READ-FDK04.

           READ FDK04 NEXT
               AT END
                  MOVE B47-MVEH-NUM OF DCPOLNA TO P06-VEH OF PWK06SUB-O
                  MOVE "NO MATCH FOR VEHICLE AND DRIVER"
                                     TO P06-DESCRIPTION OF PWK06SUB-O
                  GO TO 060-EXIT.

           IF  LS-POLICY-NUMBER NOT EQUAL A00-M4-POL-NUM
                  MOVE B47-MVEH-NUM OF DCPOLNA TO P06-VEH OF PWK06SUB-O
                  MOVE "NO MATCH FOR VEHICLE AND DRIVER"
                                     TO P06-DESCRIPTION OF PWK06SUB-O
                  GO TO 060-EXIT.

           IF  LS-POLICY-NUMBER EQUAL A00-M4-POL-NUM
               IF  B47-MVEH-NUM OF DCPOLNA = B79-M4-ITEM-SEQ
                   MOVE C52-MVEH-YEAR TO VEH-YR
                   MOVE M27-MMAKE     TO VEH-MAKE
                   MOVE M28-MMODEL    TO VEH-MODEL
                   MOVE VEH-DESC TO P06-DESCRIPTION OF PWK06SUB-O
               ELSE
                   GO TO 060-READ-FDK04.

       060-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      /
73202  075-START-NOT-LESS.
73202
73202      MOVE ZERO                   TO FDK02-STATUS.
73202
73202      START FDK02 KEY IS NOT < EXTERNALLY-DESCRIBED-KEY
73202          INVALID KEY
73202              MOVE "2"            TO FDK02-STATUS
73202              PERFORM 080-CLEAR-PWK06 THRU 080-EXIT
73202              MOVE IND-OFF        TO IN32 OF PWK06DDS-O.
73202
73202  075-EXIT.
73202      EXIT.
73202
       080-CLEAR-PWK06.
           IF SUBFILE-KEY EQUAL 13
               GO TO 080-EXIT.
           MOVE IND-ON                 TO IN30 OF PWK06SUB-O.
12097      MOVE IND-OFF TO IN29 OF PWK06SUB-O.                          TJB
13920      MOVE ZERO TO P06-DR-NUM OF PWK06SUB-O                        TJB
13920                   P06-DR-B42 OF PWK06SUB-O                        TJB
13920                   P06-VEH OF PWK06SUB-O.                          TJB
           ADD 1                       TO SUBFILE-KEY.
           WRITE SUBFILE CRTREC FROM PWK06SUB-O FORMAT "PWK06SUB".
           GO TO 080-CLEAR-PWK06.

       080-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      /***************************************************************
      *         DRIVER MENU ROUTINE    PWK06                         *
      ****************************************************************

       100-MAIN-PROCESS.

           MOVE SPACES TO WS-FEEDBACK
12097                     ERROR-SWITCH.                                 TJB
           MOVE IND-ON                 TO IN28 OF PWK06CTL-O.
           WRITE CRTREC FROM PWK06DDS-O FORMAT IS "PWK06DDS".
           WRITE CRTREC FROM PWK06CTL-O FORMAT IS "PWK06CTL".
           MOVE IND-OFF                TO IN99 OF PWK06DDS-O.
           READ SCN INTO PWK06CTL-I FORMAT IS "PWK06CTL".


           IF CFKEY-23
               MOVE "PWK06"            TO R46-HARG-BOOKNO
               MOVE SPACES             TO HELP-ROW24
               MOVE P06-ERR-MESSAGE    TO HELP-MSG
               PERFORM 999-HELP-FUNCTION THRU 999-EXIT
               GO TO 100-EXIT.

           MOVE SPACES                 TO P06-ERR-MESS-NO
                                          P06-ERR-MESSAGE.
12097      MOVE IND-OFF TO IN29 OF PWK06SUB-O                           TJB
12097                      IN33 OF PWK06DDS-O                           TJB
                           IN99 OF PWK06DDS-O.


           IF  CFKEY-1  OR  CFKEY-24 OR
               CFKEY-2 AND LS-DETAIL-INQUIRY
               GO TO 100-EXIT.

           IF CFKEY-2 AND NOT LS-DETAIL-INQUIRY
               MOVE IND-ON             TO IN27 OF PWK06CTL-O
               WRITE CRTREC FROM PWK06CTL-O FORMAT "PWK06CTL"
               MOVE ZERO               TO SUBFILE-KEY
               PERFORM 050-LOAD-DRIVERS THRU 050-EXIT
               MOVE IND-OFF            TO IN27 OF PWK06CTL-O
               GO TO 100-EXIT.

           PERFORM 400-RESET-FACS THRU 400-EXIT.

           MOVE "Y"                    TO EDIT-ERROR-SW.

           IF CFKEY-7  AND  NOT LS-DETAIL-INQUIRY
               PERFORM 150-ADD-DRIVER THRU 150-EXIT
               GO TO 100-EXIT.

           MOVE 1                      TO SUBFILE-KEY.
           IF CFKEY-3
             IF IN30 OF PWK06DDS-O EQUAL IND-ON
               MOVE IND-ON             TO IN27 OF PWK06CTL-O
               WRITE CRTREC FROM PWK06CTL-O FORMAT "PWK06CTL"
               MOVE ZERO               TO SUBFILE-KEY
               PERFORM 050-LOAD-DRIVERS THRU 050-EXIT
               MOVE IND-OFF            TO IN27 OF PWK06CTL-O
                                          IN30 OF PWK06DDS-O
               GO TO 100-MAIN-PROCESS
             ELSE
                 GO TO 100-EXIT.

           IF CFKEY-5
             IF IN31 OF PWK06DDS-O EQUAL IND-ON
               MOVE IND-ON             TO IN27 OF PWK06CTL-O
               WRITE CRTREC FROM PWK06CTL-O FORMAT "PWK06CTL"
               MOVE ZERO               TO SUBFILE-KEY
73202          PERFORM 075-START-NOT-LESS THRU 075-EXIT
               PERFORM 050-LOOP THRU 050-EXIT
               MOVE IND-OFF            TO IN27 OF PWK06CTL-O
               MOVE IND-ON             TO IN30 OF PWK06DDS-O
               GO TO 100-MAIN-PROCESS
             ELSE
                 GO TO 100-EXIT.

           IF ENTER-KEY  OR  CFKEY-10
               NEXT SENTENCE
           ELSE
               GO TO 100-EXIT.

           PERFORM 1000-FIND-CURSOR THRU 1000-EXIT.
           COMPUTE SUBFILE-KEY = ROW-RESULT - 5.
           READ SUBFILE SCN INTO PWK06SUB-I FORMAT "PWK06SUB"
                INVALID KEY GO TO 100-EXIT.

           IF P06-DR-NAME OF PWK06SUB-I EQUAL SPACES
              GO TO 100-EXIT.

           MOVE P06-DR-NUM OF PWK06SUB-I TO P07-DRIVER OF PWK07DDS-O.
           MOVE P06-DR-NUM OF PWK06SUB-I TO P08-DRIVER OF PWK08DDS-O.

           MOVE LS-POLICY-NUMBER         TO A00-M2-POL-NUM.
           MOVE LS-HISTORY-DATE          TO A30-M2-HIST-EXP-DATE.
           MOVE "DR"                     TO B25-M2-NAME-TYPE.
           MOVE P06-DR-NUM OF PWK06SUB-I TO B26-M2-NAME-SEQ OF DCPOLNA.
           START FDK02 KEY IS NOT < A00-M2-POL-NUM
                                    A30-M2-HIST-EXP-DATE
                                    B25-M2-NAME-TYPE
                                    B26-M2-NAME-SEQ OF DCPOLNA
               INVALID KEY
                   MOVE "2"            TO FDK02-STATUS.

           READ FDK02 NEXT
               AT END
                   GO TO 100-EXIT.

           IF A00-M2-POL-NUM NOT EQUAL LS-POLICY-NUMBER OR
              B25-M2-NAME-TYPE NOT EQUAL "DR"
                  GO TO 100-EXIT.
           MOVE "0"                    TO FDK02-STATUS.

           MOVE CORR DCPOLNA     TO PWK07DDS-O.
53240      MOVE MVR-REQ-SEQ-NUM OF DCPOLNA TO PASS-SEQ-NUM.
14358***   MOVE SPACES TO B55-MFIN-REAS1 OF DCPOLNA,
14358***                  B55-MFIN-RES-2 OF DCPOLNA.
           MOVE "  CHANGE"       TO P07-TRANS.

61630      MOVE X71-QUARTER-SECTION(1:1) TO PIP-REJ OF PWK07DDS-O.

           MOVE D63-IRS-NUM-1 OF DCPOLNA TO WS-D63-IRS-NUM-1.
           MOVE D63-IRS-NUM-2 OF DCPOLNA TO WS-D63-IRS-NUM-2.
           MOVE D63-IRS-NUM-3 OF DCPOLNA TO WS-D63-IRS-NUM-3.
           IF WS-D63-SOC-SEC-NUM NUMERIC
               MOVE WS-D63-SOC-SEC-NUM
                                 TO D63-SOC-SEC-NUM OF PWK07DDS-O
           ELSE
               MOVE ZEROS        TO D63-SOC-SEC-NUM OF PWK07DDS-O.

           MOVE B57-MMVR-DATE   OF DCPOLNA   TO RECORD-DATE.
           MOVE CORR RECORD-DATX TO DISPLAY-DATX.
           MOVE DISPLAY-DATE    TO B57-MMVR-DATE   OF PWK07DDS-O.
