12038  181-UPD-LAST-UNLISTED.                                           TJB
12038 *** Update the FDK01 LAST UNLISTED DRIVER ACCIDENT DATE if any    TJB
12038 *** of the FDK03 ACCIDENT DATES for the driver being deleted are  TJB
12038 *** greater than the FDK01 last date.                             TJB
12038      MOVE ZERO TO WS-SAVE-DATE.                                   TJB
53044      IF (LS-COMPANY EQUAL "05"                                    TJB
53044          OR (LS-COMPANY EQUAL "14"                                TJB
53044              AND LS-GROUP-LINE EQUAL "07"))                       TJB
