12038          MOVE B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE1 OF DCPOLVIOL TO WS-SAVE-DATE     TJB
12038      END-IF.                                                      TJB
12038      IF B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE2 OF DCPOLVIOL GREATER THAN WS-SAVE-DATE TJB
12038          MOVE B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE2 OF DCPOLVIOL TO WS-SAVE-DATE     TJB
12038      END-IF.                                                      TJB
12038      IF B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE3 OF DCPOLVIOL GREATER THAN WS-SAVE-DATE TJB
12038          MOVE B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE3 OF DCPOLVIOL TO WS-SAVE-DATE     TJB
12038      END-IF.                                                      TJB
12038      IF B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE4 OF DCPOLVIOL GREATER THAN WS-SAVE-DATE TJB
12038          MOVE B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE4 OF DCPOLVIOL TO WS-SAVE-DATE     TJB
12038      END-IF.                                                      TJB
12038      IF B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE5 OF DCPOLVIOL GREATER THAN WS-SAVE-DATE TJB
12038          MOVE B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE5 OF DCPOLVIOL TO WS-SAVE-DATE     TJB
12038      END-IF.                                                      TJB
12038      IF B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE6 OF DCPOLVIOL GREATER THAN WS-SAVE-DATE TJB
12038          MOVE B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE6 OF DCPOLVIOL TO WS-SAVE-DATE     TJB
12038      END-IF.                                                      TJB
12038      IF B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE7 OF DCPOLVIOL GREATER THAN WS-SAVE-DATE TJB
12038          MOVE B70-MDR-LOSS-DATE7 OF DCPOLVIOL TO WS-SAVE-DATE     TJB
12038      END-IF.                                                      TJB
53044  181-UPD-LAST-UNLISTED-1.                                         TJB
