      ****************************************************************
      *    ROUTINE TO DELETE DRIVERS AND VIOLATIONS                  *
      ****************************************************************

       865-DELETE-P05-RECORD.

           MOVE DCPOLNA   TO SAVE-DCPOLNAME.
           MOVE DCPOLVIOL TO SAVE-DCPOLVIOL.
           CLOSE    FDK02 FDK03.
           OPEN I-O FDK02 FDK03.
           MOVE SAVE-DCPOLNAME TO DCPOLNA.
           MOVE SAVE-DCPOLVIOL TO DCPOLVIOL.

           READ FDK02
               INVALID KEY
               MOVE ERR-FLAG TO FDK02-STATUS
               GO TO 865-EXIT.
           MOVE ERR-FLAG TO FDK02-STATUS.

      *    MOVE DCPOLNA TO DCPOLVIOL.
           MOVE SPACES  TO DCPOLVIOL.
           MOVE A00-M2-POL-NUM       OF DCPOLNA
                               TO A00-M3-POL-NUM       OF DCPOLVIOL.
           MOVE A30-M2-HIST-EXP-DATE OF DCPOLNA
                               TO A30-M3-HIST-EXP-DATE OF DCPOLVIOL.
           MOVE ZEROS          TO B94-M3-LOCATION      OF DCPOLVIOL
                                  S06-M3-BUILDING      OF DCPOLVIOL.
           MOVE B25-M2-NAME-TYPE     OF DCPOLNA
                               TO B25-M3-NAME-TYPE     OF DCPOLVIOL.
           MOVE B26-M2-NAME-SEQ      OF DCPOLNA
                               TO B26-M3-NAME-SEQ      OF DCPOLVIOL.
      *    START FDK03 KEY EQUAL EXTERNALLY-DESCRIBED-KEY
      *        INVALID KEY
      *        MOVE ERR-FLAG TO FDK03-STATUS.
      *
      *    IF RECORD-FOUND-ON-FDK03
           PERFORM 870-READ-VIOL-REC THRU 870-EXIT.
           IF RECORD-FOUND-ON-FDK03
               DELETE FDK03 RECORD
                   INVALID KEY
                   MOVE ERR-FLAG TO FDK03-STATUS.

           DELETE FDK02 RECORD
               INVALID KEY
               MOVE ERR-FLAG TO FDK02-STATUS.

           MOVE DCPOLNA   TO SAVE-DCPOLNAME.
           MOVE DCPOLVIOL TO SAVE-DCPOLVIOL.
           CLOSE      FDK02 FDK03.
           OPEN INPUT FDK02 FDK03.
           MOVE SAVE-DCPOLNAME TO DCPOLNA.
           MOVE SAVE-DCPOLVIOL TO DCPOLVIOL.

       865-EXIT.
           EXIT.
