      /***************************************************************
      *    CALL HELP FUNCTION MODULE                                 *
      ****************************************************************

       999-HELP-FUNCTION.

           MOVE IF-CLOSE TO RF-TYPE-IO.
           PERFORM 780-READ-REF-TO-EDIT THRU 780-EXIT.

           COPY FCB03.

           MOVE IF-RDRANDOM TO RF-TYPE-IO.

       999-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      /***************************************************************
      *    FIND CURSOR POSITION ON SCREEN
      ****************************************************************

       1000-FIND-CURSOR.

      *    COPYBOOK - FEEDBACK AREA FOR CURSOR POSITION
           COPY ZCB49.

       1000-EXIT.
           EXIT.

       2000-CALCULATE-DAYS.
           MOVE "G+"      TO DATE-CALL-TYPE.                            11524JLB
           CALL "DATECV" USING DATE-CALL-PARAMETERS.                    11524JLB
                                                                        11524JLB
           IF DATE-RETURN-CODE NOT EQUAL 0                              11524JLB
               MOVE "E"   TO ERROR-IND.                                 11524JLB
                                                                        11524JLB
       2000-EXIT.   EXIT.
13587 /**************************************************************** TJB
13587  9000-CENTURY.                                                    TJB
           MOVE CORR DISPLAY-DATX TO RECORD-DATX.
           IF RECORD-DATE NOT EQUAL ZERO
               AND YY OF RECORD-DATX LESS THAN CENTURY-YEAR
               ADD CENTURY-100 TO YY OF RECORD-DATX.
13587  9000-EXIT.  EXIT.                                                TJB
      /***************************************************************
      *    CALL HELP FUNCTION
      ****************************************************************

       9005-GET-HELP.

      *    COPYBOOK - CALL HELP FUNCTION
           COPY   FCB03.

       9005-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      /***************************************************************
      *    MOVE DATA FROM REFERENCE FILE TO FIELD ON SCREEN PWK07
      *    DRIVER INFORMATION
      ****************************************************************

       92000-MOVE-FROM-REF.

           IF LS-DETAIL-INQUIRY
               GO TO 92000-EXIT.

           IF HELP-RETURN-VALUE EQUAL SPACES
               AND HELP-RETURN-NUMERIC EQUAL 0
               GO TO 92000-EXIT.

           IF (ROW OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 06
               AND COP OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 27)
               MOVE HELP-RETURN-VALUE TO B45-MSEX OF PWK07DDS-O
           ELSE IF (ROW OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 06
               AND COP OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 53)
               MOVE HELP-RETURN-VALUE TO B44-MMARITAL OF PWK07DDS-O
           ELSE IF (ROW OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 07
               AND COP OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 53)
               MOVE HELP-RETURN-VALUE TO B46-MPRIN-OPER OF PWK07DDS-O
           ELSE IF (ROW OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 08
               AND COP OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 26)
               MOVE HELP-RETURN-VALUE TO B50-MLIC-STATE OF PWK07DDS-O
           ELSE IF (ROW OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 09
               AND COP OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 26)
               MOVE HELP-RETURN-VALUE TO Q75-DR-LIC-CLASS OF PWK07DDS-O
           ELSE IF (ROW OF PWK07DDS-O EQUAL 10
