      /***************************************************************
      *    DETERMINE CURSOR POSITION FOR THE HELP FUNCTION
      ****************************************************************

       95000-DETERMINE-POSITION.

           MOVE "Y"                    TO HELP-LOOKUP-SW.

           IF (ROW-RESULT LESS    THAN 08) OR
              (ROW-RESULT GREATER THAN 20)
               GO TO 95010-INVALID-CURSOR.

           MOVE ROW-RESULT             TO ROW OF PWK08DDS-O.
           MOVE COL-RESULT             TO COP OF PWK08DDS-O.

           MOVE ROW OF PWK08DDS-O      TO VALID-ROW.
           MOVE COP OF PWK08DDS-O      TO VALID-COL.
           MOVE WORK-POSITION          TO VALID-POSITION.
           IF NOT VALID-ROWCOL
                GO TO 95010-INVALID-CURSOR.

           PERFORM 95020-SET-EDIT-VALUES THRU 95020-EXIT.

           GO TO 95010-EXIT.

       95010-INVALID-CURSOR.

           MOVE "018"                  TO ELEMENT-NO.
           MOVE "IN"                   TO EDIT-NO.
           MOVE "INVALID POSTIONING OF CURSOR FOR REF. FILE LOOKUP"
                                       TO ROW24-MSG.
           MOVE "N"                    TO HELP-LOOKUP-SW.

           MOVE ERROR-KEY              TO P08-ERR-MESS-NO.
           MOVE ZEROS                  TO COP OF PWK08DDS-I
                                          ROW OF PWK08DDS-I.
           MOVE IND-ON                 TO IN99 OF PWK08DDS-O.
           MOVE ROW24-MSG              TO P08-ERR-MESSAGE.

       95010-EXIT.
           EXIT.
